0. Cannot use HOME key to reset the transformation because the range
dialogues intercept key events (see GWin2d.cc).

1. Set glClearColor().

2. Get Aux library code from ftp://sgigate.sgi.com/pub/opengl/opengl.tar.Z.

3. Doesn't Color::Color(const Color &color, double intensity) need a
"nearest pure" calculation?  (Also put in XGL version.)

4. Does double buffering require color index mode under X?
Note that RGBA mode is set in Raster.cc.
